# Chronolap

Advanced stopwatch with lap tracking for Python developers.

## Installation

```bash
pip install chronolap
```


```python

from chronolap import ChronolapTimer

timer = ChronolapTimer()
timer.start()
# your code
timer.lap("First section")
timer.stop()

for lap in timer.laps:
    print(lap)

```


